00:02:13.279 --> 00:02:16.679
that impact in your life and in my life

00:02:16.679 --> 00:02:20.520
when we hear the wonderful truth that Jesus saved,

00:02:20.520 --> 00:02:23.240
that it continues to impact our lives,

00:02:23.240 --> 00:02:25.039
that we, maybe I'll say it this way,

00:02:25.559 --> 00:02:26.800
that we never get over it

00:02:26.800 --> 00:02:30.639
and that we constantly live in a state of appreciation

00:02:30.639 --> 00:02:33.500
