00:02:57.000 --> 00:02:59.759
referenced verses in the book of 1 John.

00:02:59.759 --> 00:03:01.759
It may not be at the top of the list,

00:03:01.759 --> 00:03:04.360
but it certainly would find itself on the list

00:03:04.360 --> 00:03:08.119
