Of course, broadly speaking,

00:03:49.460 --> 00:03:52.240
it's the entirety of the book of 1 John.

00:03:52.240 --> 00:03:54.979
But as we look at this text of scripture this morning,

00:03:54.979 --> 00:03:56.860
we find that the Bible tells us,

00:03:56.860 --> 00:03:58.580
notice in verse number nine,

00:03:58.580 --> 00:04:00.660
if we receive the witness of men,

00:04:00.660 --> 00:04:01.899
then notice the statement,

00:04:01.899 --> 00:04:04.960
the witness of God is greater,

00:04:04.960 --> 00:04:06.660
for this is the witness of God,

00:04:06.660 --> 00:04:09.660
which he hath testified of his son.

00:04:09.660 --> 00:04:11.800
And we'll look at the entirety of the passage,

00:04:11.800 --> 00:04:14.460
but I want you to be aware of the fact this morning

00:04:14.460 --> 00:04:16.779
that the witness of God is greater.

00:04:16.779 --> 00:04:19.980
And I'm so thankful that God has given us

00:04:19.980 --> 00:04:21.899
this record or this witness.

00:04:21.899 --> 00:04:24.220
We'll see that both of those terms are used

00:04:24.220 --> 00:04:26.019
throughout these verses of scripture

00:04:26.019 --> 00:04:27.619
about the record that's been given,

00:04:27.619 --> 00:04:29.540
the witness that has been provided.

00:04:29.540 --> 00:04:32.679
And I'm so thankful to have the truth

00:04:32.679 --> 00:04:34.220
of the Word of God.

00:04:34.220 --> 00:04:35.739
If you're taking notes this morning,

00:04:35.739 --> 00:04:37.019
notice first of all with me,

00:04:37.019 --> 00:04:39.299
the record delivered.

00:04:39.299 --> 00:04:40.459
The record delivered.

