00:05:11.640 --> 00:05:13.920
the Spirit, and the water, and the blood,

00:05:14.760 --> 00:05:17.239
and these three agree in one.

00:05:17.239 --> 00:05:19.119
As we begin to look at these verses of scripture

00:05:19.119 --> 00:05:21.799
and understand the record has been delivered,

00:05:21.799 --> 00:05:23.359
we ought to just pause right there

00:05:23.359 --> 00:05:25.760
and say hallelujah that He's given us a record

00:05:25.760 --> 00:05:28.019
that He's provided us with this witness

00:05:28.019 --> 00:05:29.320
and it's been delivered.

00:05:29.320 --> 00:05:30.880
As we begin to think about the record

00:05:30.880 --> 00:05:32.059
that's been delivered,

00:05:32.059 --> 00:05:34.100
there are a couple of things that I understand

00:05:34.100 --> 00:05:35.480
in this passage of scripture

00:05:35.480 --> 00:05:38.660
that are important for us to recognize this morning.

00:05:38.660 --> 00:05:40.040
And number one is this,

00:05:40.040 --> 00:05:43.440
the record that's been delivered is reliable.

00:05:43.440 --> 00:05:44.679
It's reliable.

00:05:44.679 --> 00:05:46.160
Aren't you thankful for that?

00:05:46.160 --> 00:05:49.220
I don't want a record that is not trustworthy.

00:05:49.220 --> 00:05:51.600
I don't want a record that is not reliable,

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:54.660
something that I can't trust, that I cannot depend on.

00:05:54.660 --> 00:05:56.920
But when we look at the record that's been delivered,

00:05:56.920 --> 00:05:59.959
as John is writing here to these believers,

00:05:59.959 --> 00:06:03.480
he says to them, and we find by way of preservation

00:06:03.480 --> 00:06:04.959
that God is saying to us

00:06:04.959 --> 00:06:08.959
that the record that's been delivered is reliable.

00:06:08.959 --> 00:06:10.160
It is trustworthy.

00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:13.079
It is something that we stake our eternity on

00:06:13.079 --> 00:06:14.839
and we ought to rejoice this morning

00:06:14.839 --> 00:06:17.839
that we have a reliable record.

00:06:17.839 --> 00:06:20.399
Notice what the Bible says about this record.

00:06:20.399 --> 00:06:22.000
The Bible says in verse number six,

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:24.839
this is He that came by water and blood,

00:06:24.839 --> 00:06:26.279
even Jesus Christ.

00:06:26.279 --> 00:06:30.399
Notice, not by water only, but by water and blood.

00:06:30.399 --> 00:06:33.399
And then it says this, and it is the Spirit.

00:06:33.399 --> 00:06:34.880
That's a capital S.

00:06:34.880 --> 00:06:35.980
Who's it referring to?

00:06:35.980 --> 00:06:39.040
It's referring to the Holy Spirit or the Holy Ghost.

00:06:39.040 --> 00:06:43.480
And it says the Spirit that beareth witness.

00:06:43.480 --> 00:06:45.399
I'm thankful that the Spirit of God,

00:06:45.399 --> 00:06:47.440
the Holy Ghost, bears witness.

00:06:47.440 --> 00:06:51.239
And I'm thankful that because the Holy Spirit is,

00:06:51.239 --> 00:06:52.559
when we think about the Trinity,

00:06:52.559 --> 00:06:56.040
the third person of the Godhead, the Holy Ghost,

00:06:56.040 --> 00:06:59.700
and the witness that He gives is reliable,

00:06:59.700 --> 00:07:04.700
notice what it says, because the Spirit is truth.

00:07:05.700 --> 00:07:08.540
There are so many people today

00:07:08.540 --> 00:07:12.059
that are so confused about truth.

00:07:12.059 --> 00:07:13.260
Can you know truth?

00:07:13.260 --> 00:07:14.859
Is there truth?

00:07:14.859 --> 00:07:16.820
They believe that truth is something

00:07:16.820 --> 00:07:19.380
that would be described as being relative,

00:07:19.380 --> 00:07:22.579
that it's your truth or their truth or my truth

00:07:22.579 --> 00:07:24.059
or someone else's truth,

00:07:24.059 --> 00:07:26.100
but I'm thankful that the Word of God

00:07:26.100 --> 00:07:28.859
declares for us that the Spirit is truth.

00:07:28.859 --> 00:07:31.420
And remember that Jesus Christ said this

00:07:31.420 --> 00:07:33.619
in John 14 in verse number six,

00:07:33.619 --> 00:07:38.500
I am the way, the truth, and the life.

00:07:38.500 --> 00:07:41.899
No man cometh unto the Father but by me.

00:07:41.899 --> 00:07:43.380
What a great declaration.

00:07:43.380 --> 00:07:45.739
We find that the Bible says in John 17,

00:07:45.739 --> 00:07:47.380
sanctify them by thy Word.

00:07:47.380 --> 00:07:51.899
Thy Word is truth.

00:07:51.899 --> 00:07:54.559
We begin to think about the Spirit bearing witness

00:07:54.559 --> 00:07:56.820
and the Spirit being defined here

00:07:56.820 --> 00:08:00.739
as being the, because the Spirit is truth,

00:08:00.739 --> 00:08:04.100
because it is the Spirit that beareth witness

00:08:04.100 --> 00:08:06.519
and because it is the Spirit that is truth,

00:08:06.519 --> 00:08:10.019
then we know that this record that we have is reliable.

00:08:10.019 --> 00:08:12.700
It is trustworthy, it's dependable.

00:08:12.700 --> 00:08:15.179
Listen, I'm not interested in something

00:08:15.179 --> 00:08:17.820
that's just potentially reliable.

00:08:17.820 --> 00:08:19.339
I'm not interested in something

00:08:19.339 --> 00:08:21.540
that has holes and has problems.

00:08:21.540 --> 00:08:25.019
I'm thankful that God said that every Word of God is pure

00:08:25.019 --> 00:08:27.540
and that He's given us a perfect book

00:08:27.579 --> 00:08:30.980
and He's given it to us and He's preserved it for us.

00:08:30.980 --> 00:08:33.739
And we understand as we look at the passage of Scripture

00:08:33.739 --> 00:08:36.320
that there is unity and there is agreement

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:37.539
within the Godhead.

00:08:37.539 --> 00:08:39.020
It tells us in verse number seven,

00:08:39.020 --> 00:08:41.960
for there are three that bear record in heaven.

00:08:41.960 --> 00:08:44.500
By the way, I'm thankful that at this time,

00:08:44.500 --> 00:08:46.299
at the writing of the book of 1 John

00:08:46.299 --> 00:08:48.219
and even now still at this moment,

00:08:48.219 --> 00:08:50.219
that Jesus is in heaven.

00:08:50.219 --> 00:08:52.380
He's ascended up into heaven.

00:08:52.380 --> 00:08:54.219
We see that the Bible speaks about these three

00:08:54.219 --> 00:08:55.059
that bear record.

00:08:55.059 --> 00:08:57.619
The Word, the Bible says this,

00:08:57.619 --> 00:08:59.419
the Father, the Word.

00:08:59.419 --> 00:09:01.299
Who's the Word?

00:09:01.299 --> 00:09:04.179
Jesus Christ and the Holy Ghost.

00:09:04.179 --> 00:09:07.119
And these three are one.

00:09:07.119 --> 00:09:10.219
There is agreement, there is unity amongst the Trinity.

00:09:10.219 --> 00:09:12.539
And we find that Jesus Himself,

00:09:12.539 --> 00:09:15.619
after His ministry here upon this earth,

00:09:15.619 --> 00:09:17.659
after His death and His burial

00:09:17.659 --> 00:09:19.299
and His glorious resurrection

00:09:19.299 --> 00:09:20.840
and He ministered for 40 days

00:09:20.840 --> 00:09:22.659
and then He ascended up into heaven.

00:09:22.659 --> 00:09:25.000
And the Bible tells us that He's at the right hand

00:09:25.000 --> 00:09:26.320
of the throne of God

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:29.039
and that He ever liveth to make intercession for us.

00:09:29.039 --> 00:09:31.159
He was dead, but now He's alive

00:09:31.159 --> 00:09:32.760
and He's alive forevermore.

00:09:32.760 --> 00:09:35.640
And the Bible tells us that He's coming again.

00:09:35.640 --> 00:09:38.479
Oh, what a glorious truth.

00:09:38.479 --> 00:09:39.919
He has a perfect plan.

00:09:40.880 --> 00:09:43.159
We find that He's given us this record

00:09:43.159 --> 00:09:45.359
and obviously we could understand

00:09:45.359 --> 00:09:47.679
that as John is writing to these believers

00:09:47.679 --> 00:09:49.919
and under the inspiration of the Holy Spirit of God,

00:09:49.919 --> 00:09:52.599
He's writing this book of 1 John

00:09:52.599 --> 00:09:54.599
and He says that the record's been delivered,

00:09:55.159 --> 00:09:56.479
that the record is reliable,

00:09:56.479 --> 00:09:58.280
