We say, no, as those things are discovered,

00:10:15.379 --> 00:10:17.479
as those things are understood,

00:10:17.479 --> 00:10:21.959
the Bible gives credit to what they've determined.

00:10:21.959 --> 00:10:22.799
Amen?

00:10:22.799 --> 00:10:24.879
And we say the Bible is true.

00:10:25.759 --> 00:10:27.439
It's reliable.

00:10:27.439 --> 00:10:29.679
Notice, as John would write,

00:10:29.679 --> 00:10:31.079
